'''氮化釩'''，化學式為[[釩|V]][[氮|N]]的[[化合物|化合物]]。

在氮化鋼鐵以增大耐磨性時會形成氮化釩。<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1016/j.surfcoat.2005.09.026|title=Study of the wear behavior of ion nitrided steels with different vanadium contents|year=2006|author=Munozriofano, R; Casteletti, L; Nascente, P|journal=Surface and Coatings Technology|volume=200|pages=6101}}</ref> 另一相中，也被認為是氮化釩的V<sub>2</sub>N，可以在氮化過程中與VN伴生。<ref>''Thermo reactive diffusion vanadium nitride coatings on AISI 1020 steel'' U.Sen Key Engineering Materials vols 264-268 (2004),577</ref> 氮化釩為[[立方晶系|立方晶系]]，[[岩鹽|岩鹽]]結構，低溫下可形成含V<sub>4</sub>聚集的形式。<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1103/PhysRevB.38.12908|title=Structural phase transition at 205 K in stoichiometric vanadium nitride|year=1988|author=Kubel, F.; Lengauer, W.; Yvon, K.; Junod, A.|journal=Physical Review B|volume=38|pages=12908}}</ref>

氮化釩材料是種強結合的[[超導體|超導體]]。<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1103/PhysRevB.29.6198|title=Superconducting and normal-state properties of vanadium nitride|year=1984|author=Zhao, B. R.; Chen, L.; Luo, H. L.; Mullin, D. P.|journal=Physical Review B|volume=29|pages=6198}}</ref> 粒米級氮化釩晶體據稱有潛力製作成[[雙電層電容器|雙電層電容器]]。<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1002/adma.200502471|title=Fast and Reversible Surface Redox Reaction in Nanocrystalline Vanadium Nitride Supercapacitors|year=2006|author=Choi, D.; Blomgren, G. E.; Kumta, P. N.|journal=Advanced Materials|volume=18|pages=1178}}</ref>

